description:
Our "old" pal, VintageBeef, has invited us to join him on a crazy adventure, hopping from planet to planet because he can't make up his mind where we should go on vacation.

Yes that's right! We are playing the most infamous game in history, "No Man's Sky"... and for my first time. Peel off those stickers covering up the multiplayer because it actually has multiplayer now!
